name: CHEST PRESS
about: If you're looking for easy to use exercise equipment that targets your upper body, then you should try out the chest press machine.

name: BENCH PRESS
about: The bench press is a popular type of gym equipment, especially for those just starting to get into weight lifting

name: INCLINE BENCH PRESS
about: An incline bench press allows you to move the back support upwards at an angle to target your chest

name: LAT PULL DOWN
about: It's a compound exercise that specifically allows you to work on your lat muscles.

name: DUMBBELLS
about: If you're new to weight training, you will want to use dumbbells that have the lowest weight and then gradually increase from there

name: TREADMILL
about: The treadmill is mainly a cardio machine that focuses on your lower body and increase your cardiovascular endurance.
